file.name: query_06.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: OpenApi Petstoe
servers:
  - url: http://petstore.{host}.io/v1
    description: The production API server
    variables:
      host:
        default: openapi
paths:
  /pets:
    get:
      operationId: listPets
      parameters:
        - name: offset
          in: query
          schema:
            type: array
            nullable: true
            items:
              type: integer
              format: int32
      responses:
        '200':
          description: An paged array of pets
